parameters: Clerk: "Welcome. How about some hot and crispy croquettes?"
Yui: "Please give me two beef croquettes!"
Clerk: "Here you go, two beef croquettes."
Yui: "Thank you! How much do I owe you?"
Clerk: "Ah, you're a girl, so it's on the house."
Yui: "Thank you for your kindness! But I insist on paying."

Zaidar-G Combatant: "You're going to be food for Lord Itodar-G
anyway!!"
Yui: "What are you doing in a place like this--"
Zaidar-G Combatant A: "Today's catch of women is plentiful."

Zaidar-G Combatant B: "No kidding! With this many, Lord Itodar-G will
surely be satisfied."

Zaidar-G Combatant A: "If he's not full, we'll be the ones to suffer
his hunger. That guy is really scary..."

Zaidar-G Combatant B: "But seriously, the croquettes that guy makes...
they're shit awful."

Zaidar-G Combatant A: "No, the croquettes made by the original shop
owner who's locked in the warehouse were exquisite. It's just as you
say, Lord Itodar-G's croquettes are crap."

Zaidar-G Combatant B: "Hahaha, dressing up as a cook but being bad at
cooking, what a joke. It's hilarious."
Itodar-G: "I smell a young woman! Did you secure another one?"

Zaidar-G Combatant A: "Yes, exactly as you said! We've just secured a
young and cute girl!"

Itodar-G: "I'll forgive your earlier rudeness. Now hurry up and take
her to the storage room."
Itodar-G: "She'll be my dessert to enjoy later after my meal!"

Zaidar-G Combatant A & B: "Understood! We'll transport her to the
storage right away! So please don't eat us!"
Itodar-G: "Rest easy Das. Who would eat men? They taste awful."
Itodar-G: "If you don't work quickly, I'll kill you Das..."
Zaidar-G Combatant A & B: "Yes, right away!!"
There was nothing particularly new inside.
There was nothing particularly new inside.
Freshly made croquettes are lined up.
Shall we remove the fence and go inside?
The storage room is firmly closed.

Butcher: "Gufufufufu, how about a piping hot croquette? Would you like
one for the road, miss?"

Butcher: "Gufufufu, it's on the house! You can have it for free,
miss~"
Butcher: "Of course! Go ahead, eat as many as you like~"

Pony-Celeste: "No, this isn't the time for that. I need to hurry to
the Yotsukoya Department Store!"

Pony-Celeste: "Thank you for your kindness. It's very much
appreciated, but I'm in a hurry right now, so I'll come back another
time!"

???: "I let a valuable young woman slip through my fingers... I should
have just eaten her without all the fuss."

???: "That's right! If I remember correctly... Spider-G is currently
attacking Yotsukoya."

???: "As for the men, we'll turn them into combatants, and we'll have
some of the women sent over here!"
???: "But that woman just now... she had such a delicious scent."
???: "Something special that you don't feel with ordinary women..."
???: "Grrr~!! I should have eaten her right away!!!"
